{"tid":642583,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[唐姨風暴] 洪永城唐詩詠堅稱同場不尷尬 零交流無合照","createTime":"2018-04-26T01:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T06:51:41.000Z","uid":82917,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4d318f86e4d4ec658f8f130daee1bb4dae28c20c","tid":642583,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:36:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">洪撚完未呀屌你老母</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】洪永城、唐詩詠、馬國明、黃心穎與麥明詩等，昨日出席big big channel記者會。洪永城與唐詩詠這對過氣情侶成焦點，雖然二人早前已否認秘密翻撻，但詩詠日前被網友暗窒，指她不時借舊愛洪永城煲新聞；無綫昨日安排他們分開上台及分開坐，全程零交流，沒合照亦不願一齊受訪。詩詠事後稱是公司決定，不覺得被公司擺上枱，大家同一間公司同場在所難免。至於被安排上台和分開坐？她說不知道，同場也不感尷尬，亦坦言未有機會與對方傾偈打招呼。洪永城則表示到場後便一直工作，之後受訪，完全無機會跟詩詠傾偈和打招呼，並非如大家想像般尷尬，如果大家要求，合照他是沒問題的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/093537_5b75307c86677f562b7011ab2c61363c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F093537_5b75307c86677f562b7011ab2c61363c.png&h=21b046ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a69e6f1a4279ed247e4622e885a1359c339ce244","tid":642583,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:38:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/093754_a331733512b95ef2ca9ad186284a9353.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F093754_a331733512b95ef2ca9ad186284a9353.png&h=d917c9e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陰鳩公 你地睇下洪仔個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心痛"},{"pid":"e730f302e659de058217e7bb97dcde61903ce9d9","tid":642583,"uid":82917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/093858_589a59e4606afcb66b8b495f7fb8d33f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F093858_589a59e4606afcb66b8